Revision history for Colouring-In-XS

0.09    2026-03-29
        Fix SEGV when SV type is not SVt_PV in xs_ensure_obj and xs_new (e.g. hash values on older Perls).
        Fix desaturate test tolerance for floating-point rounding on i686/longdouble platforms.

0.01    Date/time
        First version, released on an unsuspecting world.

